### List all tools
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools
Accept: application/json

###

### List tools — filter by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools?category=PDF
Accept: application/json

###

### List tools — search
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools?search=qr
Accept: application/json

###

### List tools — featured only
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools?featured=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Get tool by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools/temp-mail
Accept: application/json

###

### Get tool by slug — QR
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools/qr-generator
Accept: application/json

###

### List categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Accept: application/json
